# Expo & Web (Expo Router + Netlify)

## Expo Router
- Use file-based routing under `apps/sudoku/app/*`.
- Root layout is `apps/sudoku/app/_layout.tsx`.
- Screens live under `app/<route>/index.tsx`.

## Web export
- Netlify publishes `apps/sudoku/dist`.
- Web export command is `pnpm export:web:sudoku` from the repo root (calls `expo export -p web`).
- SPA redirects are required via `apps/sudoku/public/_redirects`.

## App identifiers
- App slug: `sudoku`
- iOS bundle id: `com.cynnixstudios.sudoku`
- Android package: `com.cynnixstudios.sudoku`

